{
  "stem": "6845.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's the way it goes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after, once we were in the ghetto, we were just hoping to be taken away, because we thought the minute we are working someplace, we shall be really treated differently.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, that didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they took us away and we went in that cattle car, and I told to Nick that he should be in charge of the cattle car, so he can keep his wristwatch-- he told you, I'm sure, about the wristwatch-- that was a horrible story with him, horrible.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just horrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, at the same time, the fact that we had poison with us, that was a very comforting feeling.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had poison for Nick, myself, and for my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had a cuckoo girlfriend who didn't want to go with her own family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She just wanted to come with mine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was just sitting next-- we were just sitting on top of each other like herrings, like sardines in a box or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at one point, when Nick was taken away because of the wristwatch argument, something, and about three or four hours went by and he didn't come back, I just decided, I said, gee, for my mother to kill herself, it would be no big deal.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She tried already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's only me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't want to live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I tried to whisper to my mother, who was as close as this [POINTS] handle, that what I want to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I did barely finish one third of my sentence and my girlfriend got hysterical.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She gave out a huge scream, scream-- hysterical.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then that shook me up just fine that I'm insane.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why would I try, even to do it here in the train?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
